<i>- Retire-moi ça !</i>

475
00:42:07,685 --> 00:42:08,685
DÉCONNECTÉ

476
00:42:09,365 --> 00:42:11,045
<i>Putain, quel soulagement.</i>

477
00:42:12,205 --> 00:42:16,125
